Title: Il secondo tragico Fantozzi
Writer: Leonardo Benvenuti (screenplay), Piero De Bernardi (screenplay), Paolo Villaggio (screenplay), Luciano Salce (collaboration), Paolo Villaggio (novel)

Plot: The frustrating adventures of a humble employee who all the time has to fullfill the wishes and desires of his bosses.
